@startuml
actor "User" as User
participant "UI (Login Form)" as UI
participant "API Gateway\n(:8080)" as Gateway
participant "Auth Controller" as AuthCtrl
participant "Auth Service" as AuthSvc
participant "User Details\nService" as UserDetails
participant "JWT Utils" as Jwt
participant "User Repository" as UserRepo
database "User DB\n(PostgreSQL)" as UserDB

User -> UI: Enter username & password
UI -> Gateway: POST /api/auth/login\n(LoginRequest JSON)
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: Public path - skip JWT filter
Gateway -> AuthCtrl: POST /api/auth/login
activate AuthCtrl

AuthCtrl -> AuthSvc: authenticateUser(LoginRequest)
activate AuthSvc

AuthSvc -> AuthSvc: Create UsernamePasswordAuthenticationToken
AuthSvc -> AuthenticationManager: authenticate(token)
activate AuthenticationManager
AuthenticationManager -> UserDetails: loadUserByUsername(username)
activate UserDetails

UserDetails -> UserRepo: findByUsername(username)
activate UserRepo
UserRepo -> UserDB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
activate UserDB
UserDB --> UserRepo: User entity
deactivate UserDB
UserRepo --> UserDetails: User
deactivate UserRepo

UserDetails -> UserDetails: Build UserDetailsImpl\n(with roles & authorities)
UserDetails --> AuthenticationManager: UserDetails
deactivate UserDetails

AuthenticationManager --> AuthSvc: Authentication object
deactivate AuthenticationManager

AuthSvc -> Jwt: generateJwtToken(authentication)
activate Jwt
Jwt -> Jwt: Build JWT with subject,\nissuedAt, expiration
Jwt --> AuthSvc: JWT string
deactivate Jwt

AuthSvc --> AuthCtrl: JwtResponse(token,\nid, username, email, roles)
deactivate AuthSvc

AuthCtrl --> Gateway: 200 OK (JwtResponse JSON)
deactivate AuthCtrl

Gateway --> UI: JSON response (JWT token)
deactivate Gateway

UI -> UI: Store token in localStorage
UI --> User: Redirect to dashboard
@enduml
